#. Tag: title
#: details-tags.docbook:11
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tags"
msgstr "Oznake"

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:13
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tags provide an additional way for you to group and categorize transactions. "
"They are often useful in <link linkend=\"details.search\">searching for "
"transactions</link> and for <link linkend=\"details.reports.avail\">creating "
"reports</link>."
msgstr ""
"Oznake nudijo dodaten način za združevanje in kategoriziranje transakcij. "
"Pogosto so uporabni pri <link linkend=\"details.search\">iskanju transakcij</"
"link> in za <link linkend=\"details.reports.avail\">ustvarjanju poročil</"
"link>."

#. Tag: title
#: details-tags.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tags View"
msgstr "Pogled oznak"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-tags.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>tags view transactions tab</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>pogled oznak zavihka transakcij</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-tags.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>tags view transactions tab</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>pogled oznak zavihka transakcij</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Tags View provides information about all the tags that have been added "
"to the data file. The display is split into two areas."
msgstr ""
"Pogled oznak nudi informacije o vseh oznakah, ki so bile dodane podatkovni "
"datoteki. Zaslon je razdeljen na dve področji."

#. Tag: title
#: details-tags.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tags List"
msgstr "Seznam oznak"

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the left is a list of tags, with buttons for adding, renaming, or "
"deleting a tag."
msgstr ""
"Na levi je seznam oznak z gumbi za dodajanje, preimenovanje ali brisanje "
"oznake."

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the right you can see more detailed information about the tag selected in "
"the list on the left, in one of the two tabs: Transactions and Details. The "
"<guilabel>Transactions</guilabel> tab displays all the transactions "
"associated with the tag. The <guilabel>Details</guilabel> tab includes a "
"user-selectable color, as well as Notes, which are not used elsewhere. Note "
"that if you change the color, which is used in the symbol displayed before "
"the tag name in any associated transactions, you need to click "
"<guibutton>Update</guibutton> at the lower right of the Details area for it "
"to be saved."
msgstr ""
"Na desni si lahko ogledate podrobnejše informacije o oznaki, izbrani na "
"seznamu na levi, v enem od dveh zavihkov: Transakcije in Podrobnosti. "
"Zavihek <guilabel>Transakcije</guilabel> prikazuje vse transakcije, povezane "
"z oznako. Zavihek <guilabel>Podrobnosti</guilabel> vključuje barvo, ki jo "
"lahko izbere uporabnik, in opombe, ki se drugje ne uporabljajo. Upoštevajte, "
"da če spremenite barvo, ki se uporablja v simbolu, prikazanem pred imenom "
"oznake v kateri koli povezani transakciji, morate klikniti "
"<guibutton>Posodobi</guibutton> v spodnjem desnem kotu področja s "
"podrobnostmi, da se shrani."

#. Tag: title
#: details-tags.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding a Tag"
msgstr "Dodajanje oznake"

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As with most actions in &kmymoney;, there are multiple ways to create a new "
"tag. First, you can click the "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"tag-new.svg\" "
"format=\"SVG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> new tag icon. "
"Second, you can right-click any tag and choose <guimenuitem>New tag...</"
"guimenuitem>. This creates a new tag called <quote>New tag.</quote> See the "
"next section for how to rename the tag. Finally, you can add a new tag "
"directly in the ledger or within a split transaction by typing the name of "
"the tag in the tag field. &kmymoney; will ask if you want to add this tag "
"and after selecting <quote>yes</quote> it will be added."
msgstr ""
"Kot pri večini dejanj v &kmymoney; obstaja več načinov za ustvarjanje nove "
"oznake. Najprej lahko kliknete ikono nove oznake "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"tag-new.svg\" "
"format=\"SVG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon>. Drugič, z "
"desno miškino tipko lahko kliknete katero koli oznako in izberete "
"<guimenuitem>Nova oznaka...</guimenuitem>. To ustvari novo oznako, imenovano "
"<quote>Nova oznaka.</quote> Glejte naslednji razdelek, kako preimenovati "
"oznako. Nazadnje lahko dodate novo oznako neposredno v knjigo ali znotraj "
"razdeljene transakcije, tako da vnesete ime oznake v polje oznake. "
"&kmymoney; vas bo vprašal, ali želite dodati to oznako in po izbiri "
"<quote>da</quote> bo dodana."

#. Tag: title
#: details-tags.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Renaming a Tag"
msgstr "Preimenovanje oznake"

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To rename a tag, either click the tag name to select it and then click "
"<guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"tag-edit.svg"
"\" format=\"SVG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> Rename "
"Tag, or right-click the name and then select <guimenuitem>Rename tag</"
"guimenuitem>. The name then becomes editable. Changing the name will affect "
"the name in all the transactions in which it appears."
msgstr ""
"Če želite preimenovati značko, bodisi kliknite ime značke, da jo izberete, "
"in nato kliknite <guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"tag-edit.svg\" format=\"SVG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject "
"> </guiicon> Preimenuj značko ali z desno miškino tipko kliknite ime in nato "
"izberite <guimenuitem>Preimenuj značko</guimenuitem>. Ime je nato mogoče "
"urejati. Sprememba imena bo vplivala na ime v vseh transakcijah, v katerih "
"se pojavi."

#. Tag: title
#: details-tags.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Deleting a Tag"
msgstr "Brisanje oznake"

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To delete a tag, either select it and click <guiicon> <inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"tag-delete.svg\" format=\"SVG\"/></"
"imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> delete tag or right-click the "
"tag name and select <guimenuitem>Delete tag</guimenuitem>. If the tag has "
"any transactions, you will be presented with a dialog that allows you to "
"reassign them to a different tag."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrisati oznako, jo izberite in kliknite <guiicon> "
"<inlinemediaobject> <imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"tag-delete.svg\" "
"format=\"SVG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject> </guiicon> izbriši ali z "
"desno miškino tipko kliknite ime oznake in izberite <guimenuitem>Izbriši "
"oznako</guimenuitem>. Če ima oznaka kakršne koli transakcije, se vam prikaže "
"pogovorno okno, ki vam omogoča, da jih dodelite drugi oznaki."

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tags were introduced to &kmymoney; in version 4.7, but not all of the "
"methods for importing data are able to import tags. It is understood that "
"this is an important feature, and it will eventually be added to all import "
"methods"
msgstr ""
"Oznake so bile uvedene v &kmymoney; različice 4.7, vendar vse metode za uvoz "
"podatkov ne morejo uvoziti oznak. Razume se, da je to pomembna funkcija in "
"bo sčasoma dodana vsem metodam uvoza"

#. Tag: title
#: details-tags.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tagged transactions and Tag details"
msgstr "Označene transakcije in podrobnosti o oznaki"

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To view the transactions or view and edit the information associated with a "
"particular tag, select the tag from the list and select the appropriate tab "
"on the right side of the dialog."
msgstr ""
"Če si želite ogledati transakcije ali si ogledati in urediti informacije, "
"povezane z določeno oznako, izberite oznako s seznama in izberite ustrezen "
"zavihek na desni strani pogovornega okna."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: details-tags.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>tags view details tab</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>zavihek s pogledom oznak s podrobnostmi</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: details-tags.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>tags view details tab</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>zavihek s pogledom oznak s podrobnostmi</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: details-tags.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tagged transactions"
msgstr "Označene transakcije"

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To see a list of the transactions associated with the selected tag, select "
"the <guilabel>Transactions</guilabel> tab. This list is similar to the list "
"of transactions for a Payee. You can double-click a transaction to edit it, "
"or you can right-click the transaction and select <guimenuitem>Go to "
"'Account name'</guimenuitem> to go to the Ledgers View of that transaction "
"in the account in which the transaction has been tagged."
msgstr ""
"Za ogled seznama transakcij, povezanih z izbrano oznako, izberite zavihek "
"<guilabel>Transakcije</guilabel>. Ta seznam je podoben seznamu transakcij za "
"prejemnika plačila. Transakcijo lahko dvokliknete, da jo uredite, ali pa "
"transakcijo kliknete z desno miškino tipko in izberete <guimenuitem>Pojdi na "
"'Ime računa'</guimenuitem>, da se premaknete na Pogled poslovnih knjig te "
"transakcije v računu, v katerem je bila transakcija označena."

#. Tag: title
#: details-tags.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tag details"
msgstr "Podrobnosti oznake"

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To view and edit the information associated with a particular tag, select "
"the <guilabel>Details</guilabel> tab."
msgstr ""
"Za ogled in urejanje informacij, povezanih z določeno oznako, izberite "
"zavihek <guilabel>Podrobnosti</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can select the color used to highlight transactions with which this tag "
"has been associated. If you click the color bar, you will get a color "
"chooser dialog."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko barvo, ki se uporablja za označevanje transakcij, s katerimi "
"je bila ta oznaka povezana. Če kliknete barvno vrstico, se prikaže pogovorno "
"okno za izbiro barve."

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking the <guilabel>Closed</guilabel> checkbox will not alter any "
"transactions already associated with the tag, but it will prevent assigning "
"the tag to any additional transactions."
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete potrditveno polje <guilabel>Zaprto</guilabel>, ne boste "
"spremenili nobenih transakcij, ki so že povezane z oznako, vendar boste "
"preprečili dodelitev oznake dodatnim transakcijam."

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To modify the notes associated with the tag, just edit the text in the box."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti opombe, povezane z oznako, samo uredite besedilo v "
"polju."

#. Tag: para
#: details-tags.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are done, don't forget to click <guiicon>Update</guiicon>, at the "
"lower right of the window, although you will be prompted if you try to leave "
"the dialog without having done so."
msgstr ""
"Ko končate, ne pozabite klikniti <guiicon>Posodobi</guiicon> v spodnjem "
"desnem kotu okna, čeprav boste pozvani, če poskusite zapustiti pogovorno "
"okno, ne da bi to storili."

